<Speech gate:gateId="91850" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="91406" majorType="ParlmemberSpeechStart"><Parlmember gate:gateId="90444" majorType="speaker">ΘΕΟΔΩΡΟΣ ΔΡΙΤΣΑΣ</Parlmember>:</SpeechStart> Θα τελειώσω, κύριε Πρόεδρε. Αφήστε με, όμως, να μιλήσω.</Speech> 
